{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "66e2ffac-a616-4013-8cc5-620de74f9be4", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/66e2ffac-a616-4013-8cc5-620de74f9be4@1.pkg/1772597707830/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597708077", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/66e2ffac-a616-4013-8cc5-620de74f9be4@1.pkg/1772597707830/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597708077"}, "identifier": "66e2ffac-a616-4013-8cc5-620de74f9be4", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查优良家风的重要性。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>A：社会上的每一个人都传承家风，社会才能和谐稳定，&ldquo;仅是家族内部私德规范，与社会其他人无关&rdquo;说法错误。因此A错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>B：优良家风通过潜移默化塑造个人品格，推动社会和谐。B符合题意，因此B正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>C：&ldquo;依赖物质财富才能发挥作用&rdquo;说法错误，故C错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>D：&ldquo;不适应时代发展，在当下已经失去传承价值&rdquo;说法错误，优良家风具有超越时代的传承价值，需要不断传承，因此D错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>因此选B</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）佛山九江镇吴氏家族传承&ldquo;乐善好施&rdquo;家风，设立社区公益基金资助贫困学生；其家训《儒林乡志》记载：&ldquo;积财予孙，不如积德予人&rdquo;。这启示优良家风（ &nbsp; ）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）佛山九江镇吴氏家族传承“乐善好施”家风，设立社区公益基金资助贫困学生；其家训《儒林乡志》记载：“积财予孙，不如积德予人”。这启示优良家风（   ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/66e2ffac-a616-4013-8cc5-620de74f9be4@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754977891735", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>仅是家族内部私德规范，与社会其他人无关</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>通过潜移默化塑造个人品格，推动社会和谐</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>需要财富基础，依赖物质财富才能发挥作用</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>不适应时代发展，在当下已经失去传承价值</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）佛山九江镇吴氏家族传承&ldquo;乐善好施&rdquo;家风，设立社区公益基金资助贫困学生；其家训《儒林乡志》记载：&ldquo;积财予孙，不如积德予人&rdquo;。这启示优良家风（ &nbsp; ）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"},